                  </hi>. I live at Walliam-green, Fulham—I saw the prisoner on Friday—he had some oil and turpentine of me mixed together, but I did not sell him any plain oil.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> The bottle of oil belongs to me; I bought this oil on Thursday, and emptied it into a jar; it was on Friday night that I bought some oil and turps.</p>
